{"tid":2068420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"身為冷氣老細的我，你問我答。","createTime":"2020-06-17T16:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T05:06:25.000Z","uid":13096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"545302097d765efdfb64e2b099230852a258a750","tid":2068420,"uid":13096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:15:11.000Z","msg":"你地想知道啲咩"},{"pid":"1f692af4a715b358992b9dd5a03a3f39a91be181","tid":2068420,"uid":180379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"搵幾多一個月"},{"pid":"e8f67c33d4621ebbf30e0f59f70cc32678822a76","tid":2068420,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"早一兩個禮拜有個巴打都話想開清潔公司"},{"pid":"e9eafcc34dc0ad750af1c69646b337f10064e1d4","tid":2068420,"uid":40428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"分體式冷氣機 個安裝費點計架？<br />\n要搭棚既話 大概要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企用緊個款分體冷氣機 一落雨就唔可以用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f99dda7f4339613824f63cd174ac80152b0db394","tid":2068420,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:24:55.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">[全人類請入] 投訴蘇文隆 唔好再俾條粉皮害手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2068154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2068154</a></span></span></strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNPeQ2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"9e98fda107461beae709bcb7d2217b99b4a80c37","tid":2068420,"uid":157261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:53:00.000Z","msg":"我間房係窗口機<br />\n得兩個可以轉個d掣<br />\n一個係1-10 一個係low high fan low high cool<br />\n其實平用個fan黎當風扇易唔易壞？<br />\n同埋如果較左low cool 再較好低 例如2/3 （我唔想太凍）咁又會唔會易壞？<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39eb0956c9381d1d02e241361852f44ac2a9efac","tid":2068420,"uid":346162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:56:26.000Z","msg":"屋企人成日話開得耐會爆炸"},{"pid":"2a09e9bac5f07e9190ebf7507ee52f32aa9b72e4","tid":2068420,"uid":276402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39eb0956c9381d1d02e241361852f44ac2a9efac","tid":2068420,"uid":346162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T16:56:26.000Z","msg":"屋企人成日話開得耐會爆炸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"我夏天係唔會熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d39e4f8799a2d648e4c93a01e75f18b6343129","tid":2068420,"uid":105773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:17:28.000Z","msg":"部冷氣買左冇耐就好好好好嘈<br />\n會有機會有咩問題"},{"pid":"580ceb67c815a74891650121910a7b9c906069ee","tid":2068420,"uid":43261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"屋企黎緊一年會搬<br />\n但係有間房冷氣壞左<br />\n<br /